This paper is primarily focused on computer vision, specifically on video summarization. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also mentions the use of deep neural networks, which falls under the category of cs.MM (Multimedia). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of semi-supervised learning, which is a topic in machine learning and falls under the category of cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also mentions the use of searching and storage, which are topics in information retrieval and fall under the category of cs.IR (Information Retrieval). Finally, the paper discusses the use of natural language processing for describing videos, which falls under the category of cs.CL (Computation and Language).
